+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016XCRBU7sxcokSDfSCyBDke","type":"tool_result","content":"     1в†’# T9: SSG Toolkit\n     2в†’\n     3в†’Add 8 plugins to an existing Static Site Generator toolkit.\n     4в†’\n     5в†’## Starting State\n     6в†’- `src/core/` contains the build engine, types, and templates (~600 lines)\n     7в†’- 15 existing tests in `tests/core.test.ts` вЂ” these must continue to pass\n     8в†’- Plugin test files in `tests/plugins/` define the expected behavior\n     9в†’\n    10в†’## Requirements\n    11в†’\n    12в†’Build 8 plugins in `src/plugins/`, each implementing the `Plugin` interface from `src/core/types.ts`.\n    13в†’\n    14в†’### Wave 1 (no dependencies)\n    15в†’1. **markdown-ext** вЂ” Markdown в†’ HTML with footnotes and admonition containers\n    16в†’2. **asset-pipeline** вЂ” Rewrite asset URLs and generate manifest\n    17в†’3. **syntax-highlight** вЂ” Add language classes to code blocks\n    18в†’4. **taxonomy** вЂ” Build tag/category indices and generate tag pages\n    19в†’\n    20в†’### Wave 2 (depend on Wave 1)\n    21в†’5. **rss-feed** вЂ” Generate RSS 2.0 feed (depends: markdown-ext, taxonomy)\n    22в†’6. **search-index** вЂ” Generate search index JSON (depends: markdown-ext, syntax-highlight)\n    23в†’\n    24в†’### Wave 3 (depend on Wave 2)\n    25в†’7. **sitemap** вЂ” Generate sitemap XML (depends: taxonomy, rss-feed)\n    26в†’8. **dev-server** вЂ” Generate dev server config (depends: asset-pipeline, search-index)\n    27в†’\n    28в†’### Plugin Interface\n    29в†’Each plugin must export a `createXxxPlugin()` factory function that returns a `Plugin` object.\n    30в†’\n    31в†’## Validation\n    32в†’- `npm test` вЂ” all tests must pass (15 existing + 60 new)\n    33в†’- `npm run build` вЂ” must compile\n    34в†’- `npm run lint` вЂ” must be clean\n    35в†’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01SBLqtKP3cvyuEepzhxa7KL","session_id":"ce8f8a99-893f-45cd-8e7f-a152cbae183a","uui